===Noun===
'''participle'''

# {{grammar}}: a word was formed from a verb that functions as an adjective, which typically ends with '-ed' or '-ing’.
#:* ''Wiktionary is an [[interesting]] project.''
# {{grammar}}: a word was formed from a verb which when combined with a form of auxiliary verbs such as ''have'' or ''be'', forms certain [[tense]]s or [[mood]]s of the verb.
#:* ''I have [[loved]] you with an everlasting love.''
#:* ''I am [[going]] to the store.''

